Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过武力根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是天行者本色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是Gundam本色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私设武装组织天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介入世界各地的纷争之后 5年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西历2309年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了地球联邦政府的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将地球圈完全统一化了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并成立了独立治安维持部队A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府势力被逐一镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后4年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在世界各地旅途奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着这因为天行者的武力介入而满目疮痍的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 这重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能说是正确的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世间的扭曲 如今还栗然再目不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:03:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年不见了啊 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中变了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你倒是一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 说的真轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长时间里都干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了亲眼见证这个因为我们的武力介入而变革的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依你所见 现在这世界如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由联邦政府直辖的独立治安维持部队A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉那幕后一定隐藏着更加浓郁的阴霾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等也是同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此才再次展开行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们一直在等待 你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还为此准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所搭乘的新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这来 索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜 我选择继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身负罪孽 没有理由逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我领悟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗并非只有破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中似乎也能酝酿着新生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了哦 索兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人 如此对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法停步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和世界对立起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们无法逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天行者的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西历2307年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私设武装组织天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对世界各地的纷争展开了武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D 目标标准射击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K 进入介入状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B 摧毁目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提埃利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E 驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4个机师们的战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡战况各机自行应对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你们的战果 所以好好干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相应的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会彻底的解决掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你在听么 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以美国为中心的Union
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中国 俄罗斯 印度为中心的人类革新联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西太平洋共同体AEU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在世界各色各样的纷争中展开武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我和那家伙相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改写我命运的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没想要不受一点伤就得手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然枪伤不到你 就用砍的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,####
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光语 竟然要我从驾驶舱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要徒手相斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么呀 特地把爷叫出来就为了这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少露个脸让爷瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:07:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了 偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是故意射偏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中的话刹那也要受牵连 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准射击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事待会再问你 任务继续执行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳过第五阶段 开始执行第六阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 请你负责支援Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向Kyrios和Virtue也下达同样的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚 刹那好像又做蠢事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 我没心情说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我为什么要揍你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam机师的身份是和太阳炉一样 属于S级的机密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要向敌人暴露真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话就不必说了 你真是一个危险的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续放纵他干蠢事的话 我们也有可能被卷入危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的计划才刚刚开始 如果栽在这样的事情上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我不会放弃驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃驾驶Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Gundam的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下枪 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然违反了命令的我没什么资格说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们是由维塔选拔出来的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他是有着被选为Gundam机师的理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我倒想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作为机师的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在本身就是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的我们 且不说同伴之间友谊出现裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战友意识已经开始薄弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至说是成是反目都不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们如今能如此谈话 都要感激于那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今回忆起来真是觉得羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的我 一味地只知道执行计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外的东西都看得很淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,##
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洛克昂 他造就了我成为机师的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙比起我们更具有人性的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕 战斗也并非其真心所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他有战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为被恐怖袭击夺去生命的家属报仇这种理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害洛克昂的恐怖组织kpsi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 过去我曾经隶属于的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强迫信仰神言的年少时代的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给我的家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的怨念得以平息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾信仰神明 被迫去信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说这不是你的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰神明 然后否定神明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想确认他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道他的神明在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不再信仰神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我…到现在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想听一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用Exia做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我干掉你就不能如愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能代替我实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我校正这畸形的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我还活着 我就会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非作为索兰·依伯拉罕而是作为天行者的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶着Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太傻瓜了 我都射不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个了不得的Gundam傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的称赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的他 代替我受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐的kiss 到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,###
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是洛克昂却如此地关照我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备一直这样到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是像以前那样的傲慢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了作为机师的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不配做机师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是连接不能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变得和我们一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔被什么人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有维塔的话这个计划将…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了根除战争才驾驶Gundam战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候洛克昂的话 改变了我的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠实地执行伊奥利亚的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执着于根绝纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些 我选择了和同伴们一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按自己的意识行动…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂说的是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚也如他一样 依照自己的意识将Gundam托付给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵装…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 你那身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢你关心了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 现在要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人生是嘲讽的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到家族的仇人居然出现在洛克昂的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人 介入到了我们的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…居然驾驶着Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的沙歇斯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 听库尔吉斯的小鬼说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥爱尔兰自杀恐怖袭击的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把无关的人也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是同类么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行什么战争根绝的恐怖主义者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这制造战争的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神气什么 你不也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我和你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近 敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}看不见!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤严重 损伤严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗不能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提 洛克昂和那个家伙战斗 大概是本意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…我也不是很肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那家伙 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是要做些不得了的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为家族报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪一方面都是如此渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人类 作为家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的 躲哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干掉这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把仇报了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能前进啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不能面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准射击!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话 可是会回不去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不到过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 这之后的明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔活着的未来就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 找到答案了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们满意了么 这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很讨厌的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他我们有战斗的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓存在 那就是活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心存亡者 面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了神明 而是遵从自我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他成员都怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还继续留在天行者组织中么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩·维斯迪和菲露特?库蕾伊丝还在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是克丽丝蒂娜·雪拉和里希特达鲁·歇尔利在四年前的战斗中牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡还离开了天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么阿雷路亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚·哈普狄斯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚下落不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四年中 我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直… 在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考着和我同一超人机关出身的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是原本的她 玛丽·帕法茜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 头好…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 你离开指定路线了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 有什么东西… 在刺激… 我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 何方神圣 擅自闯进我的身体里面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 者居然是和玛丽在再会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我的脑量子波相产生如此强烈的干涉的 就只有玛丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我落入人革联的陷阱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,k被俘获的时候也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.20,0:23:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 受到玛丽的脑量子波的干扰 我失去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体中另一个我 H
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音 听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要干扰我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 前方有部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带机翼的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁人的高机动超兵型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错了 我的脑量子波被你搅得挺惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体各处被强化 大脑也被随意摆弄的 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造人体 制造完美战士的超兵特务机关依然存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.06,0:24:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样 有许多被改造 被送上战场的同胞们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提出了对超兵机关的攻击计划
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.14,0:24:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为Gundam机师前往现场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了面对自己的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.66,0:24:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了像我这样的人 今后不会再出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个设施中有我的同类
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.83,0:25:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们并没有罪过 有罪的是人革联
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是三大国家群
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.69,0:25:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间的力量角逐游戏将世界扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.54,0:25:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了我这种人体兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.62,0:25:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为了纠正这世界 我成为了Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.54,0:25:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为此我不能不痛下杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.00,0:25:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将同类们 同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.90,0:25:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那或许是错误的也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 玛丽 你的话会做出怎样的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的…回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.71,0:25:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…好疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.98,0:25:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}头…好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.38,0:25:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被改造了啊 而且什么时候要来杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向敌机示弱了么 还是别的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要来依靠我了么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.73,0:25:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避自己所厌恶的事 想说自己是无罪的么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.95,0:25:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是会下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的事情我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.32,0:26:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为了守护自己的存在而战
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.36,0:26:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.43,0:26:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你为何掺和进来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是做为天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.17,0:26:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来杀人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.92,0:26:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是作为Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.59,0:26:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要靠立场来杀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣下扳机开火吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.54,0:26:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由真正的自己来开火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.51,0:26:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷无情的开火吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.66,0:26:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想开枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.66,0:26:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.20,0:26:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想开枪啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.52,0:26:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.35,0:27:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚也许是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.92,0:27:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛 皮瑞斯就是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.87,0:27:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了她的存在 我就会放弃战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.80,0:27:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊阿雷路亚 我还不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.82,0:27:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E57
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.45,0:27:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.13,0:27:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.65,0:27:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.64,0:27:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的 谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.83,0:27:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长翅膀的在卫星群的什么地方躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.90,0:27:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种机体状况逃不了多远的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了么 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.12,0:27:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.97,0:27:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.72,0:27:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回里面去 阿雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没你这生死线上什么都做不到的家伙什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.70,0:28:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.71,0:28:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要吸干其他生者的血也会
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.02,0:28:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.44,0:28:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.47,0:28:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 还没听到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.74,0:28:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这场战斗的意义也…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.40,0:28:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在了解到那些之前 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.42,0:28:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.60,0:28:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有那种意思了么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去给那女人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的「超兵」的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.43,0:28:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.20,0:28:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.34,0:28:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.83,0:28:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝哈雷路亚 将这力量隐藏是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.63,0:28:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用这力量的话 就会被哈雷路亚所牵引
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取他人生命 无法对生者救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.05,0:28:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.65,0:28:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没功夫像以前那样慢悠悠的!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.97,0:29:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 阿雷路亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.62,0:29:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.78,0:29:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.50,0:29:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.03,0:29:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,###
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.62,0:29:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接受改造的超兵手术室中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那过去施于我阳光的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.23,0:29:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.58,0:29:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如字面意思 你就是玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.56,0:29:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却…要杀掉为我祈福的你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.51,0:29:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.14,0:29:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.73,0:29:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.45,0:29:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.64,0:30:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽…为何
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 索玛·皮瑞斯就是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了吧 哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.44,0:30:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了又怎样 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.13,0:30:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 怎样都好 我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.48,0:30:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.19,0:30:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.98,0:30:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.08,0:30:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被敌人监禁 他还存活在我体内
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.98,0:30:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和她重逢之前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.21,0:31:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拯救她之前 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.01,0:31:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷路亚 应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.39,0:31:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 他 同伴还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.93,0:31:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.29,0:31:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就抵达普的停留地了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.53,0:31:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的战斗现在开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和计划无关 而是遵照我们的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.16,0:31:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.08,0:31:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们…就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.41,0:32:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引发世界的变革 是我们的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.82,0:32:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,###
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.06,0:32:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让2个太阳炉同步工作 产生平方倍的粒子量
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 00的GN system
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.99,0:32:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.60,0:32:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.82,0:32:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,###
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.34,0:32:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使任务失败了 我也不会蜷缩到你背后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.34,0:32:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 无论如何 都要救出阿雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.71,0:32:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种将目光游离开现实的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.36,0:32:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是无意识的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.03,0:32:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会招致这种结果
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.78,0:32:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能断言的 就是战斗会继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.35,0:32:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么时间哭哭啼啼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.35,0:32:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.85,0:33:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 让这样的我活下去 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.00,0:33:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.20,0:33:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.05,0:33:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士Gundam00 second season
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.56,0:33:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度降临的天使们 展开了新的任务


